# [b][color=#4C00FF]A[/color][color=#4909FE]n[/color][color=#4613FD]y[/color][color=#431DFC]t[/color][color=#4027FB]h[/color][color=#3D31FA]i[/color][color=#3A3AF9]n[/color][color=#3744F8]g[/color] [color=#3158F6]U[/color][color=#2E62F5]p[/color][color=#2B6BF4]i[/color][color=#2875F3]c[/color][color=#267FF2]k[/color] [color=#2093F0]C[/color][color=#1D9CEF]a[/color][color=#1AA6EE]n[/color] [color=#14BAEC]H[/color][color=#11C4EB]a[/color][color=#0ECDEA]p[/color][color=#0BD7E9]p[/color][color=#08E1E8]e[/color][color=#05EBE7]n[/color][color=#02F5E6]![/color][/b] **Hosted by Icibalus and cohosted by NuclearBurrito**
*A new chapter in the Icibalus Game Cinematic Universe. I will place more time and preparation into this game than any other I have hosted. Expect greatness.*
## [b][color=#4C00FF]R[/color][color=#3C33F9]u[/color][color=#2D66F4]l[/color][color=#1E99EF]e[/color][color=#0FCCEA]s[/color][/b] - **Respect** - Respect your fellow players. I shouldn't have to explain this to you. - **Cheating** - Do not communicate with any other player outside of the game. - **Angleshooting** - Don't do it. It's unfair and nobody likes it. - **Inactivity** - Please post enough not to draw my wrath. Please. - **Mod Colours** - [b][color=#4C00FF]T[/color][color=#4A06FE]h[/color][color=#480CFD]e[/color][color=#4613FD]s[/color][color=#4419FC]e[/color] [color=#4026FB]a[/color][color=#3E2CFA]r[/color][color=#3C33F9]e[/color] [color=#383FF8]m[/color][color=#3746F7]y[/color] [color=#3352F6]m[/color][color=#3159F5]o[/color][color=#2F5FF5]d[/color] [color=#2B6CF3]c[/color][color=#2972F3]o[/color][color=#2779F2]l[/color][color=#257FF1]o[/color][color=#2485F1]r[/color][color=#228CF0]s[/color][color=#2092F0].[/color] [color=#1C9FEE]D[/color][color=#1AA5EE]o[/color][color=#18ACED]n[/color][color=#16B2EC]'[/color][color=#14B8EC]t[/color] [color=#11C5EA]u[/color][color=#0FCCEA]s[/color][color=#0DD2E9]e[/color] [color=#09DFE8]t[/color][color=#07E5E7]h[/color][color=#05EBE6]e[/color][color=#03F2E6]m[/color][color=#01F8E5].[/color][/b] - **Fun** - Not allowed. Anyone found having fun will be harshly punished.
## [b][color=#4C00FF]M[/color][color=#431CFC]e[/color][color=#3B38F9]c[/color][color=#3255F6]h[/color][color=#2A71F3]a[/color][color=#218DF0]n[/color][color=#19AAED]i[/color][color=#10C6EA]c[/color][color=#08E2E7]s[/color][/b]
- Days last for 72 hours unless shortened by majority lynch. Nights last for 24 hours. - The SoD and EoD will be set to 17:00 BST. If majority is reached, the night will be extended or shortened to reset SoD/EoD to this. - Mafia have daychat. - This game is a **Upick**. After signing up, PM me a name of a character, object or abstract philosophical concept. Your role will be based upon this name. Note: Giving me the name of a standard mafia role will not give you that role. Be warned.
## [b][color=#4C00FF]S[/color][color=#4517FC]e[/color][color=#3E2EFA]t[/color][color=#3745F7]u[/color][color=#305CF5]p[/color] [color=#228BF0]N[/color][color=#1BA2EE]o[/color][color=#14B9EC]t[/color][color=#0DD0E9]e[/color][color=#06E7E7]s[/color][/b]
- The game is set to [color=green]**13 Town**[/color], [color=red]**3 Mafia**[/color] and [color=grey]**1 Neutral**[/color]. - This game is a rolemadness game. No more than 1 player will have no special abilities. - This game may contain bastard mechanics, however this game should not be treated as a bastard game. - There are no allignment conversion mechanics in this game.
## [b][color=#4C00FF]E[/color][color=#470FFD]x[/color][color=#421FFB]a[/color][color=#3D2FFA]m[/color][color=#393FF8]p[/color][color=#344FF6]l[/color][color=#2F5FF5]e[/color] [color=#267FF2]R[/color][color=#218FF0]o[/color][color=#1C9FEE]l[/color][color=#17AFED]e[/color][color=#13BFEB]c[/color][color=#0ECFE9]a[/color][color=#09DFE8]r[/color][color=#04EFE6]d[/color][/b]

# [color=green]Exampler[/color] **Town Example Role**
You are an example role, featuring in many Forum Mafia original posts. You lead the way in being a way to show that Ici is changing his rolecard format again, and that he may or may not be copying the standard MS Upick rolecards. sigh
**Look at my format! (Example)** - Your rolecard will be published publicly before the game even begins. **Don't worry this ain't in the game (Non-existent)** - You don't actually exist in the game. **Here's how to vote someone! (Common Abilities)** - You may vote during the day.
**You win if all threats to the town have been eliminated** [/details]
